  Sailthon
  <br>
  <br>
</h1>

Sailthon is a Python module targeted at Sailfish OS Python developers.
This project aims to provide a stable API for different Sailfish OS tasks.

## Features
- Monitors cellular radio, WiFi, GPS, Bluetooth using DBUS
- Toggle Sailfish OS dialogs
- Managing files without worrying which paths are allowed on Sailfish OS
and check for file changes
- 100% Jolla Harbour compatible
